title: Salvador Dali The Disintegration of The Persistence of Memory Ornament
description:
Ornament developed from Salvador Dali’s The Disintegration of The Persistence of Memory, 1952-54. “Exclusive designs, products, images, content, publicity rights and trademarks presented herein belong to The Dalí Museum, St. Petersburg, FL. and The Gala-Dalí Foundation, Figueres, Spain.” 

Add a bit of surrealist surprise to your decorations.

  • Dimensions: 4 x 2 in.
  • Materials: Resin.
